    <description>Replaces 2 Events__c Workflow Rules:
- Event - Recon - 10/30 day alerts
- Event: Reconciliation - Recon Complete

Purpose:
Manages reconciliation lifecycle notifications for Events, including scheduled reminders and completion confirmation.

Scheduling:
- Sends a 10-day reminder email after Event_Start_Date__c
- Sends a 30-day reminder email after Event_Start_Date__c
- Scheduled paths re-check eligibility at execution time

Immediate Notifications:
- Sends &quot;Recon Complete&quot; email when Reconciliation Status changes to Reconciled.

Conditions:
- Event Start Date is in the future
- Govt Reg Price is non-zero
- Reconciliation Status is not Submitted to Finance or Reconciled</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>FR_EventStartIsTodayOrFuture</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>$Record.Event_Start_Date__c &gt;= TODAY()</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <description
    >If I were about to send a recon reminder right now, should I?</description>
        <name>FR_ReconStillPending</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>AND(
    NOT(ISPICKVAL($Record.Recon_Status__c, &quot;Submitted to Finance&quot;)),
    NOT(ISPICKVAL($Record.Recon_Status__c, &quot;Reconciled&quot;)),

    NOT(ISBLANK($Record.Govt_Reg_Price__c)),
    $Record.Govt_Reg_Price__c &gt; 0,

    $Record.Event_Start_Date__c &gt;= TODAY()
)</expression>
    </formulas>
